Ask HN: Which Companies Self-Host?
text:
I'm looking for companies that prefer self-hosting to using cloud services. I'm building a self-hosted alternative to Gitpod and Github Codespaces that works with Gitlab, Gitea, Gerrit, and any other Git provider that supports SSH. It's at https://hocus.dev if you want to check it out. I'm looking for people who would like to try it out, and I figured such companies may be interested.

What companies do you know that self-host?

Ask HN: How to get into Neurotech/BCI?
text:
I’m a nontechnical healthtech PM with a design/UX focus and a med school background, looking for advice on how to get into the Neurotech/BCI field.

I’ve scoured job listings for the top companies in the space and none seen to be looking for people on the design/UX side.

I’m curious if getting a Masters in a neuro-related discipline (neuroscience, cogsci, biomedical engineering, etc) to give me a bit more scientific and technical know-how would be wise. Unsure about its practical value.

Open to any and all advice. Thanks.
